volume.name: Roy Rogers e o Trigger: Suplemento ao Mundo de Aventuras

description:
How do you infiltrate a lost Nazi uBoat nest overrun with mercenaries? With the help of a couple of undead zombie hitmen! Basil & Moebius make one strange alliance in order to get the plans sought by their mysterious benefactor "The Collector," but what they find is a lead to an even BIGGER find...Part 3 in the 4-part adventure "The Shadow Gambit!"

Where better to hide the most dangerous weapons of the Reich than Antarctica? Basil & Moebius follow the trail to the mysterious Nazi UFO's research station, and come face to face with the Fuehrer's most insidious weapon never used! It's a race to turn the tables on their murderous -- and inhuman -- pursuers in the exciting conclusion to the 4-part adventure "The Shadow Gambit!"
name: The Shadow Gambit! Part 4

description:
Broadsword, P.I. 3

The World's Greatest Barbarian Detective continues his adventures in a weird world of hard boiled fantasy. Some comic book heroes live forever. Some die all the time. Collecting the next three stories in the "Dozen Deaths" story arc.
name: Book Three: A Dozen Deaths

description: Mags has bad dreams, and Dani is an excellent girlfriend.

Kill 'Em All

The police search Dr. Wagner's house. We find out how Vivian became addicted to Chem 19.
name: Kill 'Em All

description:
A local village girl is kidnapped to lure Rowie and Iddar to a deadly trap...

A trap set by a fanatic warlord from a once mighty Persian Empire!
Sex! Violence! Higher math! This issue has it all. Before they reach the enemy camp, our heroes must square off against sex-starved Cowgirls, bloodthirsty Deadskins, and... each other.
name: Part Four

description: Kain and his mentor, while looking into a string of strange murders being investigated by Zandalee's father, encounter a demon capable of materializing a person's fear and hellbent on slaughter. Zandalee and her mother get a visit from an unexpected guest.

Sister Long's world is turned upside down as she transitions from the relative comfort and fun of the Missionary Training Center in Utah to the struggles of a full-time missionary in Japan with only two months' worth of experience in the language.
name: Month 3: April

volume.name: DENDO: One Year and One Half in Tokyo

description:
Something Positive

Four standalone stories anchor this month's EVIL INC. Cap and Miss Match have a blow-out in the kitchen, Oliver has a playdate that goes wrong... and Iron Dragon and Desdemona had one that went right! Plus Commander Heroic gets called up to the Justice League... the bowling league, that is.

All this, plus a special bonus from the EVIL INC ARCHIVE!
name: Something Positive

description:
A Phase We're Going Through Part 2

Phase has proven an elusive foe for the Guardians. Will they be able to defeat him and catch the uncatchable?
name: A Phase We're Going Through Part 2

description: Second book in the Havenhurst series: the runaway's past catches up with her.

O.S.M.

Following the tragedy at Paradise High -- the integrated high school for Angels and humans -- police and administrators are looking for suspects, creating schoolwide tension and intrigue. But Alex sees something the rest of them do not: a clue that leads her directly into danger.
name: Paradise High Part Two of Five

description: Collecting the second volume of the classic comic adaptation of Michael Moorcock's bestselling fantasy saga, The Sailor on the Seas of Fate chronicles Elric's adventures across a supernatural sea where the lines between time and reality blur, Eternal Champions abound, and otherworldly foes threaten the very fabric of the universe!
name: Elric: The Sailor On The Seas of Fate

description: After the heart-stopping confrontation at the end of Chapter 2, Kim is removed from the investigation. But will she just return to her quiet life? And even if she wanted to... will Walter let her? Keep reading: the ending changes everything!

Music-obsessed teens struggle through the rise and Fall of Generation X and the Alternative Rock era of the 1990s. They learn that the bonds of friendship they thought were unbreakable have already begun to crack, and the music they thought they'd love forever has already started to fade.

Note: The digital edition (9/2/2015) for this issue was released before the print edition.

The world is a very big place and it's time for the LOL pups to explore!

Anpan and Nemu are two stuffed pups on a mission - to find excitement and adventure where ever they go! Whether it's a visit to the neighborhood park, vacationing in Hawaii, role-playing or taking a flight into the sky, fun and laughs are bound to follow!

Follow the gang and discover new characters in their third collection of comic strips - in full color!
name: Vol. 3: Smiles To Go!

description:
BBQ 2015

Eugene and co are visited by a group of sinister individuals who turn out to be... worse than they appear.
name: BBQ 2015

description:
The First Struggle

Within the last half hour, Thomas Simmons learned that he was burned alive and left lying in the rubble of an explosion for months. He fought a towering beast, saw the arm of a young woman re-attach itself to her body and realized his wife died while he was out cold. He had a mental breakdown and tried to run from the very people that tried to help him when suddenly the pain he had been feeling all this time got excruciating and huge blades piereced his body from inside out as a body suit grew out of him...
name: The First Struggle

description: Claire's real first day of college. Can she manage to break out of her shell and start to shine in this new environment?
Labyrinth strikes back!

Lights, Camera, Cosplay!

The 3rd issue of the Roleplayers comic series! A cosplay special issue.

It's convention season again and the roleplayers are attending a cosplay event as cosplayers! Everyone is having fun and enjoying themselves until Cassie encounters a bullying incident. Will Cassie be able to call out on the bully with the aid of her friends?

Lawrence decides to retrace his steps, revisiting each of his victims in turn and freeing their minds from the spiritual and emotional anguish the Staff of Truth has brought. But he has failed to find his son and his companion Legio shows him that not all is as it appears. The exciting conclusion to The Shepherd saga.

Chapter 12

Pat continues his search for the spell books of Dwyn.
name: Chapter 12

description: Lasha Trinity and her dog, Rover, take Lasha's new spaceship out for a cruise. While they're out, trouble is brewing on Earth. Trouble on an apocalyptic level.

The Law of Attraction

Captured by Epsilon/Fuller Group troops, Beko is taken back to New Paris for reconstruction, a process that breaks down the body into its basic components and extracts the artificial DNA.

The Occupation, an underground resistance group, is aware of Beko and have been looking for him for some time. Orphan, their leader, thinks this reconstruction process will cause destruction! He decides to attack the Epsilon/Fuller tower in the center of New Paris before Beko can be killed or cause destruction on an epic scale!
name: The Law of Attraction

description: Tara battles the Headless Horseman over Edgar Allan Poe's remains, tackles a terrifying Yeti and investigates a haunted hotel with a Shining past. Also the tragic origins of her bewitched hometown Little Salem are revealed.

Bringer of War

Mister Solenoid comes head-to-head with the madman known as Doktor Bleak, who plans to annihilate the planet in retaliation for Solenoid's attempts to upset the social order. Guest-starring the band BARENAKED LADIES in an official cameo. Chris Roberson (co-creator of iZOMBIE and EDISON REX) writes: "UNGROUNDED is a heck of a lot of fun!"
name: Chapter 3: Bringer of War

description:
Ruse

The hunt for the Father of Wolfen continues as Virgin draws closer to her prey, but can she avoid killing and succumbing to the bloodlust that she hates?
name: Ruse

description:
Mission To Mars

Ambassador Benton Hawkes tried to put his career behind him - tried to extricate himself from the pull of politicians and their corporate masters. The enemies he made sent invaders to his home - killing those close to him, and exposing a betrayal so deep he has accepted his enemies' challenge. He will go to Mars - and personally make them pay for the death and suffering they have caused.
name: Mission To Mars

description: In the final chapter of Mortal Kombat X, Sub-Zero attempts to end the cyber threat once and for alland a surprising ally joins his cause.
name: Blood Island Chapter 36: Fight To the Finish

description: Revenge and loyalty meet in Model Life Takes Shanghai. Zell is a rising fashion model and her face is all over Shanghai. Finding success is her only priority until NYC's longest-running muse, Razz, arrives in town. Between photo shoots Zell is on a mission to assist one of her best model-friends, Iso, seek revenge on Razz because Iso believes Razz killed her favorite NYC-based photographer before moving to Shanghai. Only Zell's promise to Iso is shaken when the mission proves that choosing to be true to your word can mean the betrayal toward a new friend. With each story entwining to the next, these fashion models show us beauty is just one piece of this industry of physical perfection. Isobella Jade is known as the original Mac girl for how she wrote the first draft of her modeling memoir Almost 5'4" at the Apple store in New York City. The on-going graphic novel series, "Model Life" is partly inspired by her own adventures in modeling. Despite her petite size she has pushed the boundaries and has modeled for national brands and magazines. Her ultimate underdog story has been featured in The New York Times, The Los Angeles Times, The Sydney Morning Herald, The New York Post, The New York Daily News, Publishers Weekly, Allure, Mac World UK, Mac Life, The Wall Street Journal, Glamour, Marie Claire UK, and many others. Jazmin's career started on the forefront of Urban/Street fashion in the 90s. She is a part of the K.A.Kitties fashion consulting team and has designed for nearly every American Hip-Hop Artist in existence, from The Notorious B.I.G to Nicki Minaj. This gives her art and design style a street edge. She is currently illustrating the on-going graphic novel series, 'Model Life', written by Isobella Jade.
name: Shanghai

Translates Avengers World #19.
Translates Avengers World #20.

Patience takes care of her aunties and lives humbly day to day. One day, a Dutch doctor, Julius, comes to their village for a short time to work on his book, and for a considerable salary she agrees to do housework for him. At first she finds Julius to be quite curt, but as time goes on, she finds that he's actually quite charming. Gradually, a love for him grows inside her. He also starts to unknowingly become attracted to her frankness and simple "rat" clothes...
name: Vol. 1

description:
A new student has just joined Pembrooke High, and he's turning Cheryl's life upside-down! Is she falling in love, or falling down the social ladder? She'd better figure it out fast, before she loses the class president election to him!

This digital exclusive collects the 'Queen Bee' storyline from B&V Friends Double Digest #209-212.

volume.name: Betty and Veronica's Rival Cheryl Blossom: High School Royalty

description:
The Great War, July 1917. At an isolated stretch of the Front, French and German soldiers kill each other in an endless carnage...

The night air is rent by sentries' screams. Everyone in the French camp thinks it's a trap laid by the enemy, but soon they hear screams from the German lines... With both factions being hunted, they are obliged to declare a uneasy truce and send a team of men to solve the mystery. With them goes Wohati, a Cree Warrior, one of the 12,000 Indians in the U.S. Army, and the only man who knows what's waiting out there...

volume.name: The Curse of the Wendigo: Collected Edition

description: When Meredith reaches the backwoods of Australia, where her younger sister is working, she stands dumbfounded in front of the vast land with clouds of red dust dancing around her. She understands how her sister has come to love this land and enjoys making her living here. Her sister is the opposite of Meredith, who is good at cooking and cleaning. Unfortunately for her sister, she has to leave immediately and return with Meredith to London. A dying man is waiting for her. Sadly, they are unable to convince her sister's surly and unpleasant employer, Hal, to just let her go in the middle of their contract. So before she knows it, Meredith finds herself taking her sister's place and working at the ranch...
name: Bridegroom Boss I

description: Mia, the daughter of a wealthy family, has just become the pawn in a cruel transaction. Due to the death of her older brother, her father now has no male heir. To remedy the situation, he promises his daughter's hand in marriage to a businessman named Alexander. However, this is not just an engagement, it's also a business deal. The purpose of this marriage is for a male heir. If one is born, then Alexander must deliver the boy to Mia's father, and in exchange Alexander will receive an entire island in the Aegean Sea. This arrangement that so resembles slavery makes Alexander angry, and the fact that Mia does exactly as her father says has him looking on both her and her father with disgust. Mia, however despicable the situation, complies with her father's wishes...
name: Vol. 1

description: Alex, a young female doctor, travels to Al Janeen for work. While there she angers the king, Azam, who has her thrown out of the palace for being a heretic. This is a great blow to Alex. Ever since she was a child she has dreamed of the world described in Arabian Nights. While attempting to return to her home country, she suddenly becomes entangled in a civil war, and finds herself being left behind in a mountain village--with Azam! There's no safe place for outsiders. After being unable to locate lodging, Azam suddenly gives Alex a kiss. One that she thought was like magic... Then, suddenly, he says to her, "There's only one way to overcome our current predicament. Marry me, right now."
name: Vol. 1

description: The art of comics legend Michael Turner is seen for the first time in it's original form in the new SUPERMAN/BATMAN: MICHAEL TURNER GALLERY EDITION. This spectacular new book collects the 'Supergirl' epic from SUPERMAN/BATMAN #8-13. Rounding out the book are numerous covers from IDENTITY CRISIS, JUSTICE LEAGUE OF AMERICA, THE FLASH and other DC Comics titles that helped establish Michael as an artistic force to be reckoned with. Graphitti Designs' Gallery Editions replicate the look, feel and attitude of the artwork. Every page is reproduced at original size on heavy paper stock to provide the fan and collector with museum quality reproductions obtainable nowhere else. This stunning Gallery Edition collects Michael Turner's work for DC Comics, reproduced directly from his uninked pencil art that was then enhanced and colored by the talented Peter Steigerwald. This format showcases Michael's art with all the subtleties and details that have never been captured in this fashion until now.
name: HC
